This is a collection of tools Morsulus uses to do his work.

Daud

	A Perl module that converts between Latin-1 and "Daud" notation.

xml2actions
	
	A Perl program that extracts items of interest from a Letter of
	Acceptances and Returns (LoAR) for further processing. 

Morsulus-Actions

	A Perl package that takes the output of xml2actions and creates
	an armorial database with the actions found. 

Morsulus-Ordinary-Classic

	A Perl package that implements a SQLite database schema that
	is a first step toward normalizing the Ordinary database. 

indexer

	A Perl program that presents a Tk based user interface for
	indexing armory in an Ordinary.
